'''Gayo''' or '''kayo''' is the [[Korean language|Korean]] term for [[pop music]], including [[K-pop|domestic pop]], ''[[Teuroteu|trot]]'' as well as any foreign pop music.

In [[English language|English]] usage, it is used to refer specifically to [[South Korea]]n pop music ([[K-pop]]).

